{
  "texts": [
    "However, all these systems have some drawbacks.",
    "Neural network-based summarizers produce good summaries; however, they require large volumes of data and enormous computation time.",
    "Machine learningbased systems require feature identification and selection for performing competitively.",
    "Unsupervised and graph-based methods tend to miss out on essential and fundamental features, i.e., semantics and meaning of data.",
    "Thus, we propose a domain-specific text summarizer for the biomedical domain that captures the text's underlying meaning and semantics."
  ]
}